CLASS_BARBARIAN = "Barbarians are savage warriors that value strength above all else, often hailing from savage tribal communities. Barbarians are simple and fast paced, using a quickly regenerating resource to dish out physical damage to multiple foes at once, or tear down a single foe by destroying their defences. Barbarians can dual wield weapons, or wield larger two-handed weapons to gain different benefits. Barbarians generate additional energy with each melee swing. Many abilities will apply a stacking debuff called CARNAGE to foes, which can be consumed by other abilities to make devastating attacks."
CLASS_BARBARIAN_FEMALE = "Barbarians are savage warriors that value strength above all else, often hailing from savage tribal communities. Barbarians are simple and fast paced, using a quickly regenerating resource to dish out physical damage to multiple foes at once, or tear down a single foe by destroying their defences. Barbarians can dual wield weapons, or wield larger two-handed weapons to gain different benefits. Barbarians generate additional energy with each melee swing. Many abilities will apply a stacking debuff called CARNAGE to foes, which can be consumed by other abilities to make devastating attacks."
CLASS_DEMONHUNTER = "Former servants of Illidan the Betrayer, Demon Hunters wield all-corrupting fel magics stolen from slain demons. Using their glaives, these agile warriors excel at striking down multiple foes at once using decisive strikes and infusions of demonic power. Over the course of battle, Demon Hunters generate Rage. When they fill their Rage, they will transform into a demon for a short time, drastically improving their powers. Timing this transformation can be a vital aspect of maximising the output for this class. Demon Hunters are also capable of avoiding damage with their unparalleled ability to dodge attacks, which can make them effective tanks."
CLASS_DEMONHUNTER_FEMALE = "Former servants of Illidan the Betrayer, Demon Hunters wield all-corrupting fel magics stolen from slain demons. Using their glaives, these agile warriors excel at striking down multiple foes at once using decisive strikes and infusions of demonic power. Over the course of battle, Demon Hunters generate Rage. When they fill their Rage, they will transform into a demon for a short time, drastically improving their powers. Timing this transformation can be a vital aspect of maximising the output for this class. Demon Hunters are also capable of avoiding damage with their unparalleled ability to dodge attacks, which can make them effective tanks."
CLASS_WITCHDOCTOR = "Shamanic leaders trained in the arts of voodoo, alchemy, medecine, and nature magic. Witch Doctors have an array of useful elixirs and buff effects that can aid their allies. On top of this, Witch Doctors can destroy foes using stacking curses and poisons, and dish out incremental healing to their party. These casters excel in solo play, and can sustain themselves almost indefinitely. The use of wards can provide powerful area-of-effect buffs or debuffs to foes and friends."
CLASS_WITCHDOCTOR_FEMALE = "Shamanic leaders trained in the arts of voodoo, alchemy, medecine, and nature magic. Witch Doctors have an array of useful elixirs and buff effects that can aid their allies. On top of this, Witch Doctors can destroy foes using stacking curses and poisons, and dish out incremental healing to their party. These casters excel in solo play, and can sustain themselves almost indefinitely. The use of wards can provide powerful area-of-effect buffs or debuffs to foes and friends."
CLASS_WITCHHUNTER = "Witch Hunters are stoic and dignified monster hunters that wield dual crossbows in battle, as well as dark magics which come at a price. Preferring to stay alone, Witch Hunters possess a set of skills that allow them to deal with foes without the help of a group very efficiently, through their unmatched mobility and control. Witch Hunters build up Rage with their crossbow shots, which can be used to fuel their more insidious dark magics."
CLASS_WITCHHUNTER_FEMALE = "Witch Hunters are stoic and dignified monster hunters that wield dual crossbows in battle, as well as dark magics which come at a price. Preferring to stay alone, Witch Hunters possess a set of skills that allow them to deal with foes without the help of a group very efficiently, through their unmatched mobility and control. Witch Hunters build up Rage with their crossbow shots, which can be used to fuel their more insidious dark magics."
CLASS_STORMBRINGER = "Stormbringers are wizards that wield the powers of Wind and Lightning. Many young mages are drawn to this school due to its promise of immense power, and ease to channel. Very few master this school, however, as greedy and power hungry Stormbringers are quick to meet their end. What Stormbringers lack in sustain they make up for in their enormous damage output - but this power comes at a price. As Stormbringers cast their spells, they generate Static. Static will fade over time, but if it reaches its capacity, the Stormbringer will be stunned and reduced to a near death state, leaving them vulnerable to be killed. While at high static, Stormbringers gain a buff to their damage. This is a simple class that focuses on balance in order to maximise damage output."
CLASS_STORMBRINGER_FEMALE = "Stormbringers are wizards that wield the powers of Wind and Lightning. Many young mages are drawn to this school due to its promise of immense power, and ease to channel. Very few master this school, however, as greedy and power hungry Stormbringers are quick to meet their end. What Stormbringers lack in sustain they make up for in their enormous damage output - but this power comes at a price. As Stormbringers cast their spells, they generate Static. Static will fade over time, but if it reaches its capacity, the Stormbringer will be stunned and reduced to a near death state, leaving them vulnerable to be killed. While at high static, Stormbringers gain a buff to their damage. This is a simple class that focuses on balance in order to maximise damage output."
CLASS_SPIRITMAGE = "Spirit Mages use multiple schools of magic - they are very unique, and play differently from traditional casters. Runes, portals, and ancient arcane magics are all aspects of a Spirit Mage's toolkit. Spirit Mages are the rarest form of mages in the world. Mastering this domain takes more time and patience than most people can spare. This class has access to a very wide array of control and utility effects, and is very complex and difficult to master. Spirit Mages are constantly protected by a magical barrier that causes all damage they take to be dealt to their mana pool before their health pool. While they have a large amount of Mana, the intense study required to learn this domain leaves many mages frail in their physical stature, leaving them vulnerable to attacks while their mana shield is down. When piloted by a master, the Spirit Mage's magics are some of the most destructive imaginable."
CLASS_SPIRITMAGE_FEMALE = "Spirit Mages use multiple schools of magic - they are very unique, and play differently from traditional casters. Runes, portals, and ancient arcane magics are all aspects of a Spirit Mage's toolkit. Spirit Mages are the rarest form of mages in the world. Mastering this domain takes more time and patience than most people can spare. This class has access to a very wide array of control and utility effects, and is very complex and difficult to master. Spirit Mages are constantly protected by a magical barrier that causes all damage they take to be dealt to their mana pool before their health pool. While they have a large amount of Mana, the intense study required to learn this domain leaves many mages frail in their physical stature, leaving them vulnerable to attacks while their mana shield is down. When piloted by a master, the Spirit Mage's magics are some of the most destructive imaginable."
CLASS_FLESHWARDEN = "Flesh Wardens are warriors imbued with demonic spirits, torn from the most fiery layers of hell. Devoid of any emotion but rage, these masters of demonic fire are not quick to make friends. Flesh Wardens collect Deathfire Orbs from foes to fuel their more powerful attacks. Akin to horsemen of the apocalypse, Flesh Wardens can eminate deadly pestilences to cripple foes that dare tread too close. Flesh Wardens have a great deal of self healing and damage mitigation, but are also capable damage dealers with heavy weapons. Wherever a Flesh Warden goes, they leave a trail of hellfire and bloodshed."
CLASS_FLESHWARDEN_FEMALE = "Flesh Wardens are warriors imbued with demonic spirits, torn from the most fiery layers of hell. Devoid of any emotion but rage, these masters of demonic fire are not quick to make friends. Flesh Wardens collect Deathfire Orbs from foes to fuel their more powerful attacks. Akin to horsemen of the apocalypse, Flesh Wardens can eminate deadly pestilences to cripple foes that dare tread too close. Flesh Wardens have a great deal of self healing and damage mitigation, but are also capable damage dealers with heavy weapons. Wherever a Flesh Warden goes, they leave a trail of hellfire and bloodshed."
CLASS_GUARDIAN = "Guardians are valiant and noble figures that often find themselves leading armies into war, or travelling the world protecting others from harm. Often charismatic and comitted to doing good, Guardians are most at home among trusted allies. These simple fighters are extremely capable of withstanding huge amounts of physical damage, and protecting or bolstering their comrades with War Banners. Guardians build up Inspiration as they fight, which boosts the resolve of their nearby allies. This Inspiration can also be consumed to give the Guardian's core abilities additional effects. When wielding a large weapon, a Guardian can also be a force of destruction, cutting down groups of enemies at once and paying little heed to their attacks. While Guardians possess very little self-healing, they better than any other class at preventing damage."
CLASS_GUARDIAN_FEMALE = "Guardians are valiant and noble figures that often find themselves leading armies into war, or travelling the world protecting others from harm. Often charismatic and comitted to doing good, Guardians are most at home among trusted allies. These simple fighters are extremely capable of withstanding huge amounts of physical damage, and protecting or bolstering their comrades with War Banners. Guardians build up Inspiration as they fight, which boosts the resolve of their nearby allies. This Inspiration can also be consumed to give the Guardian's core abilities additional effects. When wielding a large weapon, a Guardian can also be a force of destruction, cutting down groups of enemies at once and paying little heed to their attacks. While Guardians possess very little self-healing, they better than any other class at preventing damage."
CLASS_MONK = "Monks are devout holy fighters that focus on discipline and unarmed combat. Unarmed strikes from a Monk generate Runes which can be used to empower the Monk's blows with different kinds of energy. There are many disciplines Monks can follow, but in general they aim to attack with extreme speed."
CLASS_MONK_FEMALE = "Monks are devout holy fighters that focus on discipline and unarmed combat. Unarmed strikes from a Monk generate Runes which can be used to empower the Monk's blows with different kinds of energy. There are many disciplines Monks can follow, but in general they aim to attack with extreme speed."
CLASS_SONOFARUGAL = "Sons of Arugal are mortals afflicted with the Curse of the Worgen. Many of these people are bound to the service of Archmage Arugal, but some have broken free of his control and returned to their original lives within the Horde and the Alliance. Learning to control their power, these individuals have become valuable assets. Using blood magic, the Sons of Arugal generate Rage. At will, they may enter Worgen form, which will last until their rage is depleted. While in Worgen form they have access to an array of different melee abilities, and gain a huge boost to attack speed, but also take increased damage. This is a unique class that has a very clear burst phase which can be extended with careful strategy."
CLASS_SONOFARUGAL_FEMALE = "Sons of Arugal are mortals afflicted with the Curse of the Worgen. Many of these people are bound to the service of Archmage Arugal, but some have broken free of his control and returned to their original lives within the Horde and the Alliance. Learning to control their power, these individuals have become valuable assets. Using blood magic, the Sons of Arugal generate Rage. At will, they may enter Worgen form, which will last until their rage is depleted. While in Worgen form they have access to an array of different melee abilities, and gain a huge boost to attack speed, but also take increased damage. This is a unique class that has a very clear burst phase which can be extended with careful strategy."
