CLASS_RANGER = "There are many kinds of rangers, but many of them are either cutthroats or hunters. Excelling in both melee and ranged weapon combat, a Ranger is a versatile damage dealer. When killing beasts, Rangers collect Hide which can be used to craft temporary class-specific buffs. Beyond that, the Ranger is a simple, basic, and easy to play class that is great fit for the archer or rogue fantasy."
CLASS_RANGER_FEMALE = "There are many kinds of rangers, but many of them are either cutthroats or hunters. Excelling in both melee and ranged weapon combat, a Ranger is a versatile damage dealer. When killing beasts, Rangers collect Hide which can be used to craft temporary class-specific buffs. Beyond that, the Ranger is a simple, basic, and easy to play class that is great fit for the archer or rogue fantasy."
CLASS_PROPHET = "Disciples of Shadra, also known as Prophets or Spider Druids, are servants of the spider Loa, Shadra. They use her power to cast powerful heal-over-time effects and protective barriers. In addition to these beneficial effects, the Disciple can also transform into a spider in order to fulfil a more rogue-style niche. In this form, the Disciple can burrow underground, and surprise foes with powerful poisons. This class has an emphasis on transforming buffs/debuffs into other more powerful effects with different ability combos."
