CLASS_PYROMANCER = "Pyromancers are explosive, preferring to incinerate their foes before they even get close. With a range of interesting abilities at their disposal, Pyromancers employ a number of spell combinations in order to maximise their effect. Pyromancers can choose to summon a phoenix pet to aid them, and using their Flame Orb, they can easily control and destroy large groups of foes with ease. Pyromancers are a simple Fire magic damage dealing class, but there are a number of ways in which the class can be taken to the next level to achieve incredible results in terms of consistent damage output."
CLASS_PYROMANCER_FEMALE = "Pyromancers are explosive, preferring to incinerate their foes before they even get close. With a range of interesting abilities at their disposal, Pyromancers employ a number of spell combinations in order to maximise their effect. Pyromancers can choose to summon a phoenix pet to aid them, and using their Flame Orb, they can easily control and destroy large groups of foes with ease. Pyromancers are a simple Fire magic damage dealing class, but there are a number of ways in which the class can be taken to the next level to achieve incredible results in terms of consistent damage output."
CLASS_CULTIST = "Cultists employ the power of the Old Gods to bolster and heal their allies with eldritch magic. Cultists can summon tentacles from the ground to destroy their foes. Many of the spells in the Cultist's toolkit generate Insanity. If the Cultist reaches 100 stacks of Insanity, they will go mad, losing control of their character and running around casting random spells until they die."
CLASS_CULTIST_FEMALE = "Cultists employ the power of the Old Gods to bolster and heal their allies with eldritch magic. Cultists can summon tentacles from the ground to destroy their foes. Many of the spells in the Cultist's toolkit generate Insanity. If the Cultist reaches 100 stacks of Insanity, they will go mad, losing control of their character and running around casting random spells until they die."
CLASS_NECROMANCER = "Necromancers are dark mages that study death. Many communities are vocal about their disdain for these kinds of mages, and Necromancers normally find their only friends in others who share their passion for the dark arts. These casters use unholy magic to cast diseases and plagues upon their foes. Some Necromancer abilities generate Runic Power, which can be used to summon differnt kinds of short-lasting undead minions such as skeletons, ghouls, abominations, and even frost wyrms. The Necromancer has multiple abilities that manipulate or sacrifice their minions."
CLASS_NECROMANCER_FEMALE = "Necromancers are dark mages that study death. Many communities are vocal about their disdain for these kinds of mages, and Necromancers normally find their only friends in others who share their passion for the dark arts. These casters use unholy magic to cast diseases and plagues upon their foes. Some Necromancer abilities generate Runic Power, which can be used to summon differnt kinds of short-lasting undead minions such as skeletons, ghouls, abominations, and even frost wyrms. The Necromancer has multiple abilities that manipulate or sacrifice their minions."
CLASS_SUNCLERIC = "Sun Clerics are devout disciples of the Holy light. They are excellent healers, and are capable of defending their allies from harm with holy magic. Many of their spells generate Sunlight stacks, which increase damage and healing for a short time. Sun Clerics may also choose to follow the path of the Valkyrie Warrior, giving them the ability to wear heavy armour and use martial weapons, and granting them access to a plethora of melee combat and tanking abilities."
CLASS_SUNCLERIC_FEMALE = "Sun Clerics are devout disciples of the Holy light. They are excellent healers, and are capable of defending their allies from harm with holy magic. Many of their spells generate Sunlight stacks, which increase damage and healing for a short time. Sun Clerics may also choose to follow the path of the Valkyrie Warrior, giving them the ability to wear heavy armour and use martial weapons, and granting them access to a plethora of melee combat and tanking abilities."
CLASS_TINKER = "Tinkers are masterful inventors that use the power of their expansive minds to develop inventions that give them the upper hand in combat. Tinkers use a reload mechanic for their guns, which can hold up to 6 rounds at a time. Battle mechs, turrets, med packs, rocket boots, and other utility inventions are all crucial aspects of the Tinker's arsenal."
CLASS_TINKER_FEMALE = "Tinkers are masterful inventors that use the power of their expansive minds to develop inventions that give them the upper hand in combat. Tinkers use a reload mechanic for their guns, which can hold up to 6 rounds at a time. Battle mechs, turrets, med packs, rocket boots, and other utility inventions are all crucial aspects of the Tinker's arsenal."
CLASS_RIFTBLADE = "Riftblades are mages that were outcast from their magic schools for the study of anti-mage magic. They formed their own order, and became the world's greatest mage assassins. In the Riftblade's arsenal are a vast array of anti-magic abilities, portal magic, and elemental magic. Riftblades wield dual Runedaggers, and are highly mobile. They steal mana from their foes, and use a complex Essence system, in which the combination of different elemental essences allows the Riftblade to perform different spells. These magical rogues provide excellent utility and burst damage, and can easily surprise and destroy foes in player-vs-player combat."
CLASS_RIFTBLADE_FEMALE = "Riftblades are mages that were outcast from their magic schools for the study of anti-mage magic. They formed their own order, and became the world's greatest mage assassins. In the Riftblade's arsenal are a vast array of anti-magic abilities, portal magic, and elemental magic. Riftblades wield dual Runedaggers, and are highly mobile. They steal mana from their foes, and use a complex Essence system, in which the combination of different elemental essences allows the Riftblade to perform different spells. These magical rogues provide excellent utility and burst damage, and can easily surprise and destroy foes in player-vs-player combat."
CLASS_REAPER = "Reapers are deadly warriors that reap souls from their foes and use those souls to unleash dark magic. In addition, Reapers trade their own life force in order to perform powerful attacks with their signiature scythes. Each Reaper's scythe is the home of a malevolent spirit that controls the Reaper's actions. Reapers can drain the life of their foes to restore the life force they lose in combat. There are many ways a Reaper can be piloted. Reapers gain different passive effects depending on whether they choose to dual wield scythes, or wield a larger two-handed scythe, which opens up different avenues for play."
